-8 gmqcPE">The risk of beauty</p><p class="sc-27019820-9 cHrYLV">W Eugene Smith’s photos of the Minamata disaster are both exquisite and horrifying. How might we now look at them?</p><p class="sc-27019820-0 sc-27019820-10 jHrogk iRyBtd">Joanna Pocock</p></div><div class="sc-27019820-4 dNuwpm"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/how-prairie-philosophy-democratised-thought-in-19th-century-america"><div class="sc-27019820-7 IoTqw"><div type="essay" class="sc-4c9ef492-2 eTKecW"><img alt="Painting of two men sitting in a barn, one on a bench and the other on a chair, with a horse and pumpkins in the background." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-over-enoch-wood-perry-dt9052.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8ebcd964-91c6-4cb9-ad66-77deb816b1ad/test-essay-talking-it-ove